textAnnotations.description:
NAKASERO - BOMBO ROAD
N.B.- The two portions of the plan of Road on either side
of the line XX should be disjoined at the point where this
line crosses Road. The N.point given at foot refers to the
first portion (from Nakasero to XX), while the second portion
(from XX to Bombo) is referable to the n. point shown in red.
Land and Survey Office,
Entebbe, 20th.July 1908.
PROTECTO
CORAL
GANDA
20 JUL 1003
SURVEY
Y DEPART

WOMAT 86
